{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778377763543,"sessionID":"ses_1f06ce9c2ffeq0AGBe8JsXuCBd","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_xPikUTcNWGIM8ipl1YeA8tMq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"**Uberon term**\\nsecondary visual cortex\\n\\n**Suggested revision of textual definition**\\n\\ndef: \\\"A functional part of the visual cortex that plays a crucial role in the integration of information from various visual modalities and contribute to higher-order visual functions, including colour, object recognition and spatial awareness.\\\" [ISBN:978-0-323-10027-4, ISSN:0072-9752, WikipediaVersioned:Visual_cortex&oldid=1268682728]\\n\\n**Other issues**\\n\\nI see that there is a redundant 'part of' some 'occipital lobe' axiom there too \\nThere already is 'part of' some 'visual cortex', and 'visual cortex' is 'part of' some 'occipital lobe'\",\n3:   \"comments\": [],\n4:   \"title\": \"[Text Def] UBERON:0022232 secondary visual cortex has no textual definition\",\n5:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3471\"\n6: }\n\n(End of file - total 6 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"**Uberon term**\\nsecondary visual cortex\\n\\n**Suggested revision of textual definition**\\n\\ndef: \\\"A functional part of the visual cortex that plays a crucial role in the integration of information from various visual modalities and contribute to higher-order visual functions, including colour, object recognition and spatial awareness.\\\" [ISBN:978-0-323-10027-4, ISSN:0072-9752, WikipediaVersioned:Visual_cortex&oldid=1268682728]\\n\\n**Other issues**\\n\\nI see that there is a redundant 'part of' some 'occipital lobe' axiom there too \\nThere already is 'part of' some 'visual cortex', and 'visual cortex' is 'part of' some 'occipital lobe'\",\n  \"comments\": [],\n  \"title\": \"[Text Def] UBERON:0022232 secondary visual cortex has no textual definition\",\n  \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3471\"\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778377763530,"end":1778377763543}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0bc1c101528c42420169ffe4237cb081a38125a502633c3603"}},"id":"prt_e0f932aba0012FRt7UTtR44BUq","sessionID":"ses_1f06ce9c2ffeq0AGBe8JsXuCBd","messageID":"msg_e0f93245c001htadtB4SfyyKOJ"}}
