{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778377807324,"sessionID":"ses_1f06ce9c2ffeq0AGBe8JsXuCBd","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_yKjA0Oa7XPPvfLQYXXk1DOTQ","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Update File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0022232.obo\n@@\n id: UBERON:0022232\n name: secondary visual cortex\n+def: \"A functional part of the visual cortex that plays a crucial role in the integration of information from various visual modalities and contributes to higher-order visual functions, including colour, object recognition, and spatial awareness.\" [ISBN:978-0-323-10027-4, ISSN:0072-9752, WikipediaVersioned:Visual_cortex&oldid=1268682728]\n xref: EMAPA:35758\n xref: MA:0000915\n is_a: UBERON:0035014 {source=\"cjm\"} ! functional part of brain\n relationship: capable_of_part_of GO:0007601 ! visual perception\n relationship: overlaps UBERON:0006473 ! Brodmann (1909) area 18\n relationship: part_of UBERON:0000411 {source=\"cjm\"} ! visual cortex\n-relationship: part_of UBERON:0002021 {source=\"MA\"} ! occipital lobe\n+property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3471\" xsd:anyURI\n \n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nM terms/UBERON_0022232.obo","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0022232.obo\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0022232.obo\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/terms/UBERON_0022232.obo\n@@ -1,11 +1,11 @@\n [Term]\n id: UBERON:0022232\n name: secondary visual cortex\n+def: \"A functional part of the visual cortex that plays a crucial role in the integration of information from various visual modalities and contributes to higher-order visual functions, including colour, object recognition, and spatial awareness.\" [ISBN:978-0-323-10027-4